SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT f.FO_EMAILREPLENISHMENT) FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("KE_WSE_REPLENISHMENT") ?> r JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("KE_FORNITORE_DATA_EXP") ?> f ON r.CODICE_FORNITORE = f.FO_ID_FORNITORE WHERE r.STATUS = 'Under Approval' AND f.FO_EMAILREPLENISHMENT IS NOT NULL

SELECT FO_EMAILREPLENISHMENT FROM ( SELECT FO_EMAILREPLENISHMENT, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY FO_EMAILREPLENISHMENT) AS row_num FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT f.FO_EMAILREPLENISHMENT FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("KE_WSE_REPLENISHMENT") ?> r JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("KE_FORNITORE_DATA_EXP") ?> f ON r.CODICE_FORNITORE = f.FO_ID_FORNITORE WHERE r.STATUS = 'Under Approval' AND f.FO_EMAILREPLENISHMENT IS NOT NULL ) distinct_emails ) numbered_emails WHERE numbered_emails.row_num = #PRJ_WSE.COUNT_APPR_REPLENISHMENT;
